title: 820-01700-A DB549 Pad is gone
message: I got a 820-01700-A in on which the diode DB549 and the solder pad of Pin2 are missing. I have problems reconstructing the solder pad. I can't put a wire bridge anywhere because the line goes directly to UB400 Pin81. How important is this diode? Can the diode be left out?

title: 820-01700-A DB549 Pad is gone
message:
Board should work without it, but no protection anymore on that line.
Use original Apple charger, in this case...
